1) Extend the "Simple FM w/ GUI Index and C:M ratio controls" program from this week's code examples to implement a cascade multiple-modulator instrument, similar to that shown in the cascade diagram.\
2) Starting from the model given in the last of this week's code examples "dCarSModEnv", create one or more FM SynthDefs whose parameters are controlled by other envelope generator SynthDefs. Write a Routine that plays notes automatically, but at changing speeds (you could create your own GUI with sliders to control the speeds manually). Adjust the AutoGui and/or your own GUI controls as the Routine plays, and record the results to make a piece.
